{"tid":609592,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"分享最近釣魚心得","createTime":"2018-03-29T07:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T17:28:58.000Z","uid":22589,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"324b954086e3a523efaee4dcdff9f7e339cf9bcf","tid":609592,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:17:06.000Z","msg":"我既心得係。唔使買桿既 <br />\n<br />\n一個八磅魚排。一包鈎。一袋鉛。兩條蟲。一把刀。夠玩半日 <br />\n<br />\n首先執齊以上裝備。去七仔買半打藍妹。 <br />\n行過街市斬半隻燒鵝。 <br />\n<br />\n去就近碼頭霸個靚位。 <br />\n<br />\n隊罐啤食隻脾先 <br />\n<br />\nD骨就掉落海引d魚 <br />\n之後就開壇落鉛幫鈎。一條蟲切十份 <br />\n咁你就有廿份餌。 <br />\n之後就掉落海等。當然。過程中不忘隊啤食燒鵝同隔離d釣友吹水。吹得幾個字一扯！ <br />\n<br />\nOk kick石！ <br />\n<br />\n扯斷收返上黎又綁過。 <br />\n如是者十次八次用晒你d鉛同埋鈎之後。你d啤酒同燒鵝都所餘無幾（骨照舊掉落海引魚） <br />\n咁你就可以食埋隻鵝，飲埋罐藍妹，執埋d垃圾。有剩d蟲就比隔離or掉落海。 <br />\n之後拎返個冇左一半絲既魚排 <br />\n返去同屋企人講 <br />\n「刁。今日（落雨/冇落雨/大太陽/冇太陽）。成個海都冇魚 。」"},{"pid":"beaefcaf270751d407df027e44bd89e9728bd57e","tid":609592,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:30:22.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"7cf304092c656c38489406a4ebae0699a74ba211","tid":609592,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"=3="},{"pid":"e4e374ecae4af7df9bdce16befab1e6bf521e389","tid":609592,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cf304092c656c38489406a4ebae0699a74ba211","tid":609592,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"=3="},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"肉酸"},{"pid":"b5f6d055004177bb073820a6177d9f2e81210f95","tid":609592,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4e374ecae4af7df9bdce16befab1e6bf521e389","tid":609592,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cf304092c656c38489406a4ebae0699a74ba211","tid":609592,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"=3="},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:53:38.000Z","ms